### 调用本地Qwen3模型
POST http://127.0.0.1:18024/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "你好"
    }
  ],
  "temperature": 0.7,
  "max_tokens": 512,
  "stream": false
}

### 计算token消耗
POST http://127.0.0.1:18024/tokenize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "这是模型自己算出来的Token，和你聊天、生成时消耗完全一致"
}

### token转回原始文本
POST http://127.0.0.1:18024/detokenize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tokens": [
    100346,
    104949,
    99283,
    69103,
    104355,
    3323,
    3837,
    33108,
    56568,
    105292,
    5373,
    43959,
    13343,
    104997,
    100372,
    101266
  ]
}